snippet.textDisplay:
How I found out who sings "all the good girls go to hell":
Three days ago sitting at my computer, kinda down I pulled up Carpool Karaoke cuz it makes me happy and there she was. Watching it my 1st thought was great voice, 2nd was old soul trapped in that kid, then about 11 or so minutes in I fell in love with her mother, and realized thats where Billie and Fin got their cool, and where she got her grounded heart.
Treat your mamma well Billie she gave you your best friend, and taught you both a little bit of magic of and for the heart, and that is everything you need.
Thank you James for being and creating one of the things that makes me happy when I'm down.
Peace
snippet.textOriginal:
